{"tid":1489871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港區人大取消參觀新疆「再教育營」，同香港局勢發展有關","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:35:27.000Z","uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5fe3ffe27b94bdcc71572d44314507d6abebf43","tid":1489871,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】港區人大代表原本周四（15日）啟程去新疆考察9日，行程包括參觀新疆「再教育營」，但噚日守護香港大聯盟舉行記招講今日嘅集會，包括全國人大常委譚耀宗、港區人代陳勇、吳秋北等都有現身，原來佢哋無去到新疆。有港區人代同Emily講，因為反修例風波仲未平息，所以個考察團取消咗。<br />\n<br />\nEmily問過團長馬逢國，佢話考察團只係推遲，唔係取消，至於幾時再起行就未有定案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/20434_4135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F20434_4135.jpg&h=c30dbb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n團長馬逢國話推遲考察團係綜合考慮，主要係由人大秘書處聯絡局決定，因為呢段時間起行未必係適當時候，團中好多人都係香港意見領袖，而家香港局勢唔穩定，佢哋要留港「發揮作用」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/13143058/image1565677835201.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F13143058%2Fimage1565677835201.png&h=58971895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢又話，港區人代中都有好多社團領袖，呢排要搞集會等，所以要留港去唔到，有人要請假、有人要遲到早走、有人覺得為難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2018/09/21/20180921-071537_U13403_M455364_43c4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F20180921-071537_U13403_M455364_43c4.jpeg&h=931c527c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於係咪同參觀「再教育營」太敏感有關，馬逢國就話參觀教育營同香港無關，所以唔係敏唔敏感嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dialoguechina.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/600_phpxdZSJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dialoguechina.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F600_phpxdZSJb.jpg&h=4d50e9d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06ba63830518135cce03f6c18040cc51fc44d58a","tid":1489871,"uid":155137,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗參觀 香港好快有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}